<h1 class="text-center">Privacy Policy of the Workplace Management System</h1>
<p>Jared Anderson is the operator of the Workplace Management System web application. This web application is used to 
    improve the efficiency of a workplace, and in doing so, it requires that certain information is collected from user 
    accounts.
</p>
<p>Required information that is collected from a user account is an email and password. Adding a phone number is optional, and it can be added to a user account after registration. 
    The passwords that are created for each new account are hashed in a database to protect passwords from data mining.
</p>
<p>Cookies may be used if a user decides to have the application remember their information. </p>
